These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: spanish, pakistani, indian, egyptian, mexican, malaysian, american
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: tennis, swimming, snowboarding, lacrosse, ice-hockey, soccer, cricket
 1. the spanish is between the egyptian and the american##2
 2. the pakistani is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the mexican is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the egyptian##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the american##1
 9. the mexican is on the left of the malaysian##1
10. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the malaysian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | spanish | american | pakistani    | indian | mexican   | malaysian    |
| Sport         | soccer  | swimming   | lacrosse | tennis | snowboarding   | cricket | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pear, peas, raspberry, pepper, papaya, broccoli, eggplant
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, canadian, argentine, egyptian, brazilian, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating raspberry is between the person eating broccoli and the colombian##2
3. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the argentine##1
5. the person eating peas is in the middle##1
6. the brazilian is on the left of the nigerian##1
7. the french is on the left of the person eating peas##1
8. the person eating papaya is on the left of the egyptian##1
9. the person eating pepper is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | papaya | raspberry | broccoli | peas | eggplant | pear      | pepper  |
| Nationality   | colombian | egyptian  | french     | argentine     | brazilian  | nigerian | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, argentine, indonesian, malaysian, colombian, nigerian, japanese
7 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, guinea-pig, ferret, hedgehog, snake, chinchilla
 1. the colombian is on the left of the thai##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is the japanese##1
 4. the indonesian is on the left of the nigerian##1
 5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the malaysian is the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the thai is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the chinchilla and the malaysian##2
 9. the thai is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
10. the argentine is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | japanese | colombian | thai | argentine   | malaysian | indonesian | nigerian |
| Pet           | hedgehog | snake     | goldfish     | guinea-pig | ferret   | lizard   | chinchilla    |

