.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, mirinda, almond-milk, cola, 7up, coffee
There are 7 different nationalities: egyptian, turkish, italian, dutch, indonesian, japanese, american
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the indonesian##1
 3. the japanese is on the right of the dutch##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the indonesian##1
 5. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the dutch is between the person drinking mirinda and the japanese##2
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 8. the dutch is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the turkish##1
10. the egyptian is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | cola  | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate  | coffee      | 7up       | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | indonesian | dutch | japanese | american | egyptian | italian | turkish  |

