.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, reggae, techno, electronic, r&b, salsa, hip-hop
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, bus, boat, snowmobile, taxi, quad-bike
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of reggae##1
3. the person driving the roller is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of pop##2
4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of pop##1
7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan of electronic##1
9. the fan of r&b is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | r&b | pop | techno | hip-hop      | reggae      | salsa |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi | quad-bike       | roller | bus | snowmobile | boat |

