.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, photographer, analyst, dressmaker, librarian, architect, social-worker
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, tennis, skateboarding, surfing, rugby, sailing
1. the analyst is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the librarian##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the photographer is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the architect is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is surfing and the freelancer##2
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
8. the architect is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | librarian | freelancer | dressmaker | architect | photographer | analyst     | social-worker |
| Sport   | tennis   | skateboarding    | sailing    | surfing      | ice-hockey  | cricket | rugby |

