.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, almond-milk, 7up, mirinda, water, juice
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, climbing, soccer, sailing, ice-hockey, badminton, golf
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is golf##2
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking mirinda##2
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | tea    | 7up | almond-milk   | water | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | sailing | basketball | golf    | climbing | ice-hockey    | soccer | badminton  |

