.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, sprite, coffee, 7up, milk, tea
The people have 7 different jobs:  entrepreneur, engineer, architect, pilot, chef, journalist, videographer
 1. the chef is on the left of the pilot##1
 2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the architect##1
 3. the journalist is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the chef is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking tea##2
 7. the engineer is on the right of the journalist##1
 8. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
11. the chef is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | 7up   | soy-milk         | iced-tea     | tea              | milk    | coffee     |
| Job        | journalist | engineer | chef | pilot | videographer | entrepreneur | architect |

