.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: time-travel, crime, scientific, drama, documentary, comedy, western
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, ship, jet-ski, van, boat, snowmobile, bike
1. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the boat##2
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
8. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
9. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | drama     | comedy | documentary | scientific | western  | time-travel |
| Transport     | jet-ski | van | boat   | scooter     | bike    | ship | snowmobile   |

