.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, juice, sprite, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, water
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, rock-climbing, filmmaking, dancing, video-games, chess, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is chess##2
9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | lemonade       | water         | almond-milk         | sprite   | juice        | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby      | skydiving | filmmaking | baking | video-games | rock-climbing | chess | dancing  |

