.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-11::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, traveling, gardening, chess, camping, sudoku
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, surfing, badminton, biathlon, snowboarding, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | sudoku | camping       | traveling    | chess | gardening | card-games     | board-games       |
| Sport   | rugby    | badminton | snowboarding | biathlon        | surfing | cricket | basketball |

