.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, action, drama, superhero, romance, adventure, family
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, dubstep, classical, techno, blues, trance
 1. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of trance##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the fan of hip-hop##2
 4. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching romance movies##2
 5. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is the fan of techno##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
10. the fan of classical is the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | scientific | action  | romance   | adventure | family | drama |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | trance       | hip-hop | dubstep | blues  | ambient   | techno   |

