 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the fan of blues and the person drinking coffee##2
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking water and the person drinking coffee##2
 5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 7. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
