.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-14::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, potatoade, soy-milk, coffee, mirinda, almond-milk, 7up
There 7 different types of food: radish, cherry, artichoke, asparagus, potato, lime, tomato
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 2. the person drinking potatoade is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is the person eating radish##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 6. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is the person eating lime##1
 8. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking mirinda and the person eating artichoke##2
10. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Beverage   | coffee   | soy-milk | potatoade | sprite   | mirinda   | almond-milk     | 7up  |
| Food       | radish | potato    | asparagus  | lime | cherry | tomato | artichoke |

