 5. the person eating avocado is the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person eating apple is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person eating peach is the person eating peach##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
10. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
