6. the musician is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
7. the designer is on the right of the analyst##1
8. the doctor is between the person eating asparagus and the musician##2
9. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
| Food   | orange | kiwi    | papaya | asparagus | grapes              | apple      | pineapple    |
